Description: Citing al-Tirmidhi
---
\‘Anyone who is ignorant of the nature of servantship (ubûdiyyat) is yet
more ignorant of the nature of lordship (rubûbiyyat)', i.e., whoever does not
know the way to knowledge of himself does not know the way to knowledge of God.
